title: Crude suicide rate in Vietnam 2000 to 2015
summary: The statistic shows the number of Crude per Vietnam that the survey respondents spend on 2000 Crude on average in the Vietnam from 2000 to 2010 .
In 2005 , that number was at 6.5 Crude per Vietnam .
gold: This statistic shows the crude suicide rate in Vietnam from 2000 to 2015.
In 2015 , the crude suicide rate in Vietnam was approximately 7.4 deaths per 100,000 inhabitants .
